{"type": "article", "id": 14853, "title": "Swing灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-14T07:09:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000310Ed8OKxmWztPoU92F.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t意大利的设计工作室 Metrocuadro Design 擅长做手工灯，他们又做了一盏像折纸一样的灯 Swing。白天不需要开灯时是白色的，很素雅，晚上打开灯，灯罩内的彩色图案就能透出来，散发出幽静而迷人的光。加上灯本身的折纸感，极有趣味。灯罩采用了特卫强材料，内侧图案由 ALL THE FRUITS 绘制。售价79.2欧，<a href=\"http://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/swing-suspension-white-lamp/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142248jri8PxZEXctVkCSd.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142249xGoMclFtub2r0Ewe.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261422493twyDX7jlBHUZFIb.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}